---
title: Salade Provençale au Halloumi with Citrus Salad, Radishes & Wonton Strips
description: For this delightful dinner salad, you'll season cubes of halloumi (a sturdy grilling cheese that crisps up on the outside as it gets melty on the inside) with herbes de Provence and sear them until golden. The seared cheese is set atop a perfectly balanced green salad with peppery radishes and juicy orange slices tossed with a bright Dijon-citrus dressing and garnished with a shower of wonton strips for crunchy contrast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/685a827bd12c14cd4da5f567-72fb6a91.jpeg
